	<h3>News</h3>

<p>
	2023-02-27 Our preprint <b>Uncoiled affine Temperley-Lieb algebras and their Wenzl-Jones projectors</b> written with Alexi Morin-Duchesne is available online <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2302.12782">arXiv:2302.12782</a>!
	It defines finite-dimensional quotients of the affine and periodic Temrperley-Lieb algebras and construct Wenzl-Jones idempotents for them. It is a quite colourful reading with many diagrams.
</p>

