	<p>
		2022-11-11 Our new preprint with Christoph Müßig and Érika Róldan-Roa <em>Complexity of chess domination problems</em> is out at  <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2211.05651">arXiv:2211.05651</a> ! It proves NP-completeness of a few problems of domination
		by queens and rooks on polycubes. It also boasts a companion <a href="https://www.erikaroldan.net/queensrooksdomination">video game</a> and the solver we present 
		was used to extend <a href="	https://oeis.org/A075324">A075324</a>.	
	</p>	
	
