	<h3>Mundane and trivia</h3>
		<p>
			I pronounce my first name Aleksi but also quite like Alexeï. I pass the time, amongst other activities, by reading, playing chess and swimming. Topics that might make me speak for too long include: 
			typography, government systems, late medieval European period, the Cathar heresy in Occitan, chess history, books,
			Émile Zola, Québec gins, Simone de Beauvoir and stories from <em>Dwarf Fortress</em>. <!--If that seems interesting to you, more is available in my <a href="/blog/">personal blog</a>.-->
